OL,3,CAppeal for mother after newborn baby
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FDetectives have launched an appeal to
OL,7,Ffind a mother after a newborn baby was
OL,8,Ffound dead.
OL,10,FThe child, believed to be a girl, was
OL,11,Fdiscovered in an industrial site in
OL,12,FStation Road, Rowley Regis, just
OL,13,Fbefore midday on Thursday (June 25).
OL,15,FThe baby was found within a waste
OL,16,Fpile, which had been transported by a
OL,17,Fprivate waste operator.
OL,19,FAt this stage, police believe the baby
OL,20,Fwas unknowingly transported on
OL,21,FWednesday this week.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
