FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782735501
OL,3,CAppeal for mother after newborn baby
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police are carrying out
OL,7,Finquiries, including forensic
OL,8,Fexaminations, to identify the girl and
OL,9,Fascertain how she died.
OL,11,FThey said they're urgently trying to
OL,12,Flocate the baby's mother as they are
OL,13,Fconcerned for her welfare. She may
OL,14,Falso need any care, help, or treatment
OL,15,Fof her own, the force said.
OL,17,FThe police said: "You may be a mother,
OL,18,Ffather, friend, teacher or lecturer
OL,19,Fwho has spotted a loved-one who has
OL,20,Fbehaved differently recently."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782735501
OL,3,CAppeal for mother after newborn baby
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FThey added that they need anyone who
OL,7,Fcan help them find the mother to come
OL,8,Fforward so they can offer her support
OL,9,Ffrom our specialist staff.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police, Detective Chief
OL,12,FInspector Kylie Westlake said: "While
OL,13,Fwe don't yet know what has happened,
OL,14,Fwhat we do know is that there must be
OL,15,Fa mother out there who is in real need
OL,16,Fof help  and she is our absolute
OL,17,Fpriority at the moment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782735501
OL,3,CAppeal for mother after newborn baby
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,F"We have been checking CCTV and
OL,7,Fspeaking to hospitals, but it may be
OL,8,Fthat the mother or someone who knows
OL,9,Fwho she is sees this appeal.
OL,11,F"I really want to speak to her to make
OL,12,Fsure she's OK, and to ensure that she
OL,13,Fcan get the help that she urgently
OL,14,Fneeds."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
