PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782735501
OL,3,CAppeal for mother after newborn baby
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,F"We'll treat information we receive
OL,7,Fsensitively, and we'd ask for anyone
OL,8,Fwho can help us identify who baby and
OL,9,Fmother was to come forward. It may be
OL,10,Fyou live near a baby, and their
OL,11,Fmother, who have unexpectedly not been
OL,12,Fseen for a number of days."
OL,14,FMore to follow.
